extends layout.jade

block content
  header(class='post-header')
    h2(class='post-title') Run submission
  div(class='post-description')
    p.
      Each token can be used for <span class="important">one submission every 24 hours</span> 
      per sub-task.
      
    p.
      Since we do not make public which part of the test data
      is used for this leaderboard, we expect your runs to contain results 
      for all test cases.
      During the computation of the public leaderboard missing 
      test cases are ignored.
      If your submission contains less than half of the public test cases, it will
      not be evaluated.
      
    p.
      Don't forget to choose the correct sub-task for your submission.
    
    p.
      Expected file format (per line): <b>hash;latitude;longitude</b>
      
    p.
      If the leaderboard records an 'NaN' for your run, double-check the
      sub-task you selected (does it match the submission?) and the
      format of your submission.

    form(action="runSubmission", name="runSubmission", method="post", enctype="multipart/form-data", class='pure-form pure-form-stacked')
      fieldset
        div(class='pure-content-group')
          label(for='token') Token
          input(type="text", id="token", name="token")
        div(class='pure-content-group')
          label(for='token') Run file
          input(type="file", id="runFile", name="runFile")
        div(class='pure-content-group')
          label(for='evalType') Sub task
          select(id='evalType', name='evalType')
            option(value='locale') Locale
            option(value='mobility') Mobility
        div(class='pure-content-group')
          label(for='submit') Warning: upload can be slow, be patient!
          input(type='submit', id='submit', name='submit', value='Upload \& Evaluate', class="pure-button pure-button-primary")
    